{
  "stem": "20405.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, when they shoot somebody in the back of the head, the knees bended, and the body goes in the back, not in the front.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why the one was holding the guy by the ear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the German was shotting him, he used to push him like this, so the body was going at the front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And right away, somebody else, it was with a hose of water, cleaning the blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So somebody was coming again, the same story, the same story, same story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It happened me to be one day over there, and I didn't know that I had to push the man not to fall in the back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And usually, the men who was down, the German, they says-- they told us, or he told us-- he was very friendly with us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That gunner says, was very friendly, smoking together, giving us a cigarette, or give him a cigarette, very friendly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was something else, because all the other ones, they was hitting us with a stick, with a bat, stick, what they call it?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What they call them, this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like a baton, like a truncheon?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody or limps or cannot--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cane.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So all the-- those Germans, they were hitting us with a cane on the head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were getting away so quickly because our head was becoming so enlarged from the-- from the cane.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this guy was the only one who was so friendly with us, and the only one when they would come in 200 or 300s of those people to get killed, this guy was the first one to go and kill them.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was something [? unbelievable. ?] So friendly with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were-- we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
